thread.title: Kathy
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Kathy

author: Kathy
title: Kathy
text: Getting a taxibox made moving so much easier for us. We were in a small house and had nowhere to store boxes as we were packing up - it was great to be able to put them in the taxibox and have them out of the way. Taxibox were great to deal with and made everything so easy - even when I had to make changes to the arrangements once or twice, it was no problem. Would highly recommend taxibox!
